de.rub.dks.signal.generator

Class Signal

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.rub.dks.signal.generator.Signal

  • public abstract class Signal
extends java.lang.Object
    Signal provides functions for generating basic signals like, sine-curves, rectangular, sawtooth, triangle and one-/zero-series.
    Since:
    01.07.2014
    Version:
